{
  "_comment": [
    "Version matrix for the regtest chain builder.",
    "Each entry maps a network upgrade to the zcashd version used for that phase.",
    "",
    "VERSION SELECTION RULE: For each NU, use the latest zcashd release that",
    "(a) supports that NU's consensus rules and (b) was released before the",
    "NU activated on mainnet. This simulates the real-world wallet upgrade path.",
    "",
    "VERIFIED: All versions and download URLs confirmed against",
    "https://github.com/zcash/zcash/releases and https://download.z.cash/downloads/",
    "",
    "WALLET FORMAT: All versions use Berkeley DB for wallet.dat (ZIP 400).",
    "There is no SQLite migration within zcashd.",
    "",
    "DOWNLOAD URL PATTERNS:",
    "  v1.0.x - v2.0.x: zcash-{VERSION}-linux64.tar.gz (no distro suffix)",
    "  v2.1.0-1 - v4.1.1: zcash-{VERSION}-linux64-debian-stretch.tar.gz",
    "  v5.0.0: zcash-{VERSION}-linux64-debian-buster.tar.gz",
    "  v6.0.0+: zcash-{VERSION}-linux64-debian-bullseye.tar.gz or -bookworm"
  ],
